{"ID":270292, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"292\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs291.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs293.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 292<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">the beasts giving glory to God,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> and understood them. God who made the beasts could understand\n  every language spoken by them. The four beasts<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> were four of the most noble animals that had filled\n  the measure of their creation,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and had been saved from other worlds, because they were perfect:\n  they were like angels in their sphere. We are not told where they came from, and I do not know; but\n  they were seen and heard by John praising and glorifying God.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The popular religionists of the day tell us, forsooth, that the beasts spoken of in the Revelation\n  represent kingdoms. Very well, on the same principle we can say that the twenty-four elders spoken\n  of represent beasts; for they are all spoken of at the same time, and are represented as all uniting in\n  the same acts of praise and devotion.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">This learned interpretation is all as flat as a pancake! &ldquo;What do you use such vulgar expressions\n  for, being a prophet?&rdquo;  Because the old women understand it&mdash;they make pancakes. Deacon\n  Homespun said the earth was flat as a pancake, and ridiculed the science which proved to the\n  contrary. The whole argument is flat, and I don&rsquo;t know of anything better to represent it. The world\n  is full of technicalities and misrepresentation, which I calculate to overthrow, and speak of things\n  as they actually exist.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Again, there is no revelation to prove that things do not exist in heaven as I have set forth, nor\n  yet to show that the beasts meant anything but beasts; and we never can comprehend the things of\n  God and of heaven,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> but by revelation.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> We may spiritualize and express opinions to all eternity; but\n  that is no authority.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Elders to Preach Repentance and Let Mysteries Alone<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Oh, ye elders of Israel,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> hearken to my voice;<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> and when you are sent into the world to preach,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span>\n  tell those things you are sent to tell; preach and cry aloud,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> &ldquo;Repent ye, for the kingdom of heaven\n  is at hand;<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> repent and believe the Gospel.&rdquo;  Declare the first principles, and let mysteries alone,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span>\n  lest ye be overthrown. Never meddle with the visions of beasts and subjects you do not understand.\n  Elder Brown, when you go to Palmyra, say nothing about the four beasts, but preach those things\n  the Lord has told you to preach about&mdash;repentance and baptism for the remission of sins.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110717\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110717)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110717)\">Rev. 4:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110734\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110734)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110734)\">Rev. 5:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110713\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110713)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110713)\">Rev. 4:6,8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114522\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114522)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114522)\">D&amp;C 77:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114815\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114815)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114815)\">D&amp;C 88:19,25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110714\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110714)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110714)\">Rev. 4:8-9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110715\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110715)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110715)\">Rev. 4:8-9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110722\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110722)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110722)\">Rev. 5:8-9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112822\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112822)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112822)\">Morm. 9:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114844\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114844)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114844)\">D&amp;C 88:49<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114481\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114481)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114481)\">D&amp;C 76:90<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108981\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108981)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108981)\">Acts 4:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113575\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113575)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113575)\">D&amp;C 33:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115992\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115992)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115992)\">D&amp;C 124:45<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108488\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108488)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108488)\">Luke 9:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112019\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112019)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112019)\">Alma 24:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113634\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113634)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113634)\">D&amp;C 36:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113967\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113967)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113967)\">D&amp;C 50:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107085\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107085)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107085)\">Isa. 24:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107255\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107255)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107255)\">Isa. 58:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116040\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116040)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116040)\">D&amp;C 124:101<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107767\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107767)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107767)\">Matt. 3:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108310\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108310)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108310)\">Mark 1:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111672\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111672)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111672)\">Mosiah 18:19-20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113303\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113303)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113303)\">D&amp;C 19:21,31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108302\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108302)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108302)\">Mark 1:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112220\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112220)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112220)\">Alma 37:33-34<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113312\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113312)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113312)\">D&amp;C 19:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}